SUMMARY:Dancing On The Waterfront
DESCRIPTION:Dancing on the Waterfront – Saturday Social! 💃🕺\nJoin us Saturday from 5 PM to 9 PM for an evening of Salsa\, Bachata\, Kizomba\, and Brazilian Zouk by the water!\n💲 Donations Appreciated!\nThis is a FREE community event\, but your support helps cover instructors\, DJ\, photography\, and park service fees.\n🎶 Schedule:\n🕔 5:00 PM – Free Class with instructor Stephen Jackson\n🕺 Social Dancing begins immediately after!\n📍 Location:\n📌 3300 Water Street\, NW – Georgetown\, Washington\, DC\nWalk directly across the street towards the water’s edge\, and you’ll find us dancing!\n🚗 Parking:\n• Garage parking next 3200 Waters Street NW /(The Flour Mill Garage) $12.00 and garage parking next to Mr. Smith’s restaurant (3205 Water St NW) – $19 all day\n• Side street parking available (Park at your own risk)\n🍹 BYOD & Dining Options\nWe cannot sell drinks at DOTW\, but feel free to BYOD or enjoy a picnic at the nearby lawn! Plenty of restaurants are across the street for food and drinks.\n🎂 Birthday Dances\nWant a special birthday dance? Let us know!\n📲 Morris Jackson: (301) 717-2390\n💃 Dance Classes\nFor class details\, contact:\n📲 @steviejdance or call (610) 333-6408\n🎧 DJ Services\n📲\n📸 Photography Services\n📲 @sharonann.photography or call (240) 339-5160\n📞 Questions? Contact our host:\n📲 Morris Jackson – (301) 717-2390 or @mjacks1992\n🎥 Filming & Photography Notice\nBy attending\, you consent to being photographed and recorded for promotional use on social media\, websites\, and advertising.\n📲 Follow us on Instagram and Facebook:\n📌 @dotw_georgetown @dancingafterdark_dmv\n🔥 See you on the dance floor! 🔥
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/dancing-on-the-waterfront/2026-04-04/
LOCATION:3300 Water St NW\, 3300 Water St NW\, Washington\, DC\, DC\, 20007\, United States
CATEGORIES:Washington DC-Baltimore
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golatindance.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Dancing_outdoors_ad9030777b.jpeg
END:VEVENT
