SUMMARY:Funky Mambo Monthly Friday @Leaf & Cane - Salsa Night in the City
DESCRIPTION:🎶 Funky Mambo @ Leaf & Cane – Salsa Classes & Party 💃🕺 \nGet ready\, London! 🌆 Funky Mambo – the city’s premier Mambo school – is teaming up with the vibrant Latin cocktail bar Leaf & Cane 🍹 to bring you an exciting new monthly Friday Salsa Night right in the heart of the City. \nJoin us for Funky Mambo @ Leaf & Cane – a night of rhythm\, fun\, cocktails\, and dancing 🥳🔥 – perfect for kicking off your weekend in style! \n📍 Venue: Leaf & Cane\, Hyatt Regency\, 19 New Bridge St\, London EC4V 6DB\n🚉 Just 1 min from Blackfriars Station\n✨ Latin American-inspired bar with handcrafted cocktails 🍸\, premium rums 🥃\, delicious food 🍴 & an outdoor terrace 🌿\n*Salsa Special Drink Menu! – Discount on selected drinks when you show your wristband at the bar. \n🗓 Upcoming 2026 Dates: \n🎉 Fri\, 27 February ft. DJ Julian Summers\n🥳 Fri\, 13 March\n🎶Fri\, 10 April (TBC)\n💃 Fri\, 15 May (TBC)\n🕺🏻Fri\, 12 June (TBC)\n🫶 Fri\, 10 July (TBC)\n💥 Fri\, 14 August (TBC)\n✨️ Fri\, 11 September (TBC)\n👠 Fri 9 October (TBC)\n🪘Fri 13 November (TBC)\n🎄Fri\, 11 December (TBC) \n🕖 Evening Schedule: \n7:00pm – Registration opens 📝\n7:15pm – FREE 30-min Intro Salsa Class (Absolute beginners welcome! 🙌)\n8:00pm – Salsa Classes with Funky Mambo 🏆\n9:00pm–Midnight – Party & Social Dancing with top Salsa DJs 🎧💃 \n💷 Pricing:\n£15 – Classes + Party\n£10 – Party Only \nTickets available online at Ticketlab & Eventbrite\, or CASH only at the door – no card payments. \nPARKING\n1. Street Parking\nTudor Street and the surrounding areas are mostly single yellow lines\, so it’s free after 6:30 p.m.\nNo congestion charge after 6 p.m. \n2. Baynard House Car Park\nThe Hyatt Regency (where the event is) suggests this parking spot: \nhttps://www.hyatt.com/hyatt-regency/en-US/lonrb-hyatt-regency-london-blackfriars/parking-and-transportation \nBaynard House Car Park\nhttps://share.google/3zgrwFwoui3ZD2uWl \nIt’s open 24/7.\nOn Fridays after 7 p.m.\, it’s a one-time payment of £4.50 – £7.30 (depends on your car). \n🏍🚲 Motorcycles and bicycles — complimentary in designated bays. \n============ \nWhether you’re brand new to Salsa or already dancing in your sleep 😴🕺\, this is your chance to enjoy top-quality classes\, meet fun people\, and dance the night away 💫 in one of London’s most stylish hidden gems. \n👠 Grab your friends\, your dancing shoes\, and let’s Mambo under the city lights! 🌃✨ \n📲 Follow @FunkyMamboUK & @LeafAndCane on Instagram & Facebook for updates\, vibes & videos. \n🔥 See you on the dancefloor! \n#SalsaParty #SalsaLondon #SalsaClasses #FreeSalsa #SalsaLesson #SalsaSocial #FridaySalsa #FunkyMambo #LeafAndCane #Brackfrias #SalsaInTheCity #SalsaDancing
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/funky-mambo-monthly-friday-leaf-cane-salsa-night-in-the-city-ft-dj-julian-summers/2026-04-10/
LOCATION:Hyatt Regency Leaf & Cane\, 19 New Bridge St\, London\, ECAV 6DB\, United Kingdom
CATEGORIES:London
END:VEVENT
