DESCRIPTION:Join us for a night of non-stop salsa at Changó in Maida Vale\, W9 – just a short walk from Warwick Avenue or Royal Oak stations. \nSALSA SOCIAL — 8:00pm to 11:30pm \nNo classes\, no interruptions – just pure\, continuous dancing! \nBrought to you by Cali Beat\, our social is 100% salsa\, featuring authentic Latin music all night long. \nExpect great energy\, friendly dancers\, and an atmosphere that celebrates true salsa culture. \nLOCATION: The Amadeus\, 50 Shirland Rd London W9 2JA (Short walk from Warwick Avenue & Royal Oak stations) \nCome for the music\, stay for the energy – and let Changó bring the salsa magic. \nPlease note this purely a social only with no classes\, and there is no bar\, but BYOD 🙂 \nEntry is £10 online or £12 on the door. \nFull info and online tickets at changosalsa.com
