SUMMARY:LATIN PARADISE SALSA & BACHATA MONTHLY PARTY
DESCRIPTION:LATIN PARADISE SALSA & BACHATA SPECIAL PARTY \nOur regular Fridays become a party on the Second Friday of every month. Experience an unforgettable Salsa & Bachata Party at Crofton Halls\, Orpington\, with the added bonus of free parking. \nWe kick off the night with Salsa & Bachata lessons. If you’re new to dancing\, we recommend joining our beginners’ group. All levels are welcome! No prior experience or dance partner is needed. Many attendees come solo\, and we rotate partners throughout the lesson\, giving you the chance to dance with different people. If you’d prefer to stay with your own partner for the entire class\, just let the teacher know\, and we’ll be happy to accommodate you. \nSchedule:\n– 🕖 8:00 PM: Salsa (Cross Body) Lessons – All Levels\n– 🕗 9:00 PM: Bachata Lessons – All Levels\n– 🕘 10:00 PM – 12:00 AM: Party Time! \nAt Latin Paradise and other Latin parties\, we play both Salsa and Bachata\, Even if you’ve never heard of bachata before\, we can’t recommend it enough! It’s a lot of fun\, and most beginners find it even easier than salsa. \nDJ: The incredible Dj Papi will keep you moving all night long with the best Salsa and Bachata tracks. \n📍Venue:\nCrofton Halls\nYork Rise\nOrpington\, BR6 8PR\nOpposite Orpington Train Station \nIf you’re looking for a Salsa club in London\, you’re in the right place. \nCome dance\, learn\, and enjoy the lively atmosphere at Latin Paradise!
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/latin-paradise-salsa-bachata-monthly-party/2026-04-10/
LOCATION:Crofton Hall Orpington\, York Rise\, London\, BR6 8PR\, GB
CATEGORIES:London
END:VEVENT
